ReturnPolicy.Description:
Returns:
There are no returns on any items that are sold as bullion or contain GOLD, SILVER, PLATINUM or PALLADIUM and are sold based on market prices.  These products are sold based on current market prices and are not returnable. If you are unsure if an item is subject to this NO RETURN policy, please contact us.
To make a return:
Your item must be in its original unused condition to be returned. You must return the item within 14 days of your purchase. 
1)      Please contact us to request a refund and we will assign you a Return #.
2)      Mail your returned item to:
         Yazi Shedbalkar
         830 West Northwest Highway
         Suite 12
         Palatine, IL 60067
3)      Refunds will be issued via PayPal once the items have been received properly.

 Return Exceptions:   If the Listing shows NO RETURNS, then the items cannot be returned.

Please be aware that we require a phone number for all purchases.  This is to help us to resolve issues in a more efficient manner.
Our Privacy Statement can be found at http://www.pgsgoldandcoin.com/privacy-statement/


Combined Shipping:
Our system will automatically combine shipping if you purchase multiple items as long as the multiple purchases are completed and paid for before the first invoice is generated or the first item is shipped.  Invoice Generation and Shipping is normally done as soon as possible, so to be sure to receive combined shipping, please contact us immediately after purchasing your first item and let us know not to ship it until you are completed.
